## Limitations

The analysis is limited by the availability of historical records and the subjective interpretation of cultural norms from the past. Additionally, while technological advancements are well-documented, cultural perceptions are more challenging to quantify and may vary across different regions and social classes. The findings are based on interpretations from available literature and may not encompass all possible explanations.

